518
00:35:21,790 --> 00:35:22,820
Nemyslíš?

519
00:35:29,550 --> 00:35:31,410
Um... Právnik Shin?

520
00:35:32,600 --> 00:35:34,020
Náhodou...

521
00:35:34,460 --> 00:35:38,110
