528
00:36:00,450 --> 00:36:02,310
Ty fagan!

529
00:36:02,310 --> 00:36:05,240
Vieš, aké bolo pre mňa ťažké to vyčistiť?!

530
00:36:05,240 --> 00:36:07,250
Ty fagan... Ty fagan!

