574
00:38:18,620 --> 00:38:21,460
a kvôli týmto pochybnostiam ho zbavil viny.

575
00:38:21,470 --> 00:38:25,080
Presne tak! Ten verejný obhajca som bol ja.

576
00:38:25,080 --> 00:38:26,180
Bol som to ja!

577
00:38:26,220 --> 00:38:29,090
