583
00:38:43,700 --> 00:38:46,340
Pretože sme nakoniec chytili pravého vinníka!

584
00:38:46,720 --> 00:38:48,280
Chytili ste pravého vinníka?

585
00:38:48,280 --> 00:38:49,410
Áno.

586
00:38:49,410 --> 00:38:50,930
Chytil sa pravý vinník.

587
00:38:51,310 --> 00:38:54,480
