782
00:54:33,360 --> 00:54:35,100
Alebo bude zranený niekto iný.

783
00:54:36,980 --> 00:54:40,230
Ak by som to mala byť ja... Som naozaj sklamaná.

784
00:54:41,510 --> 00:54:45,950
Že si myslíš, že som taká slabá a patetická.

785
00:54:47,460 --> 00:54:48,660
Dobre teda.

786
00:54:48,660 --> 00:54:50,600
Zistím si to sama.

787
00:54:51,670 --> 00:54:53,260
Reportér Park Joo Hyuk je...

788
00:54:54,100 --> 00:54:55,700
Park Soo Haov otec.

789
00:54:57,290 --> 00:54:59,380
Babka s Alzheimerom a vnuk

790
00:55:00,010 --> 00:55:03,670
sú Min Joon Gookova matka a jeho syn.

791
00:55:05,390 --> 00:55:07,460
Ten, kto ti to poslal...

792
00:55:08,950 --> 00:55:10,560
Je Min Joon Gook.

793
00:55:22,710 --> 00:55:23,840
Soo Ha.

794
00:55:24,860 --> 00:55:25,910
Tu máš.

795
00:55:26,510 --> 00:55:28,760
Naozaj ste to našiel. Ďakujem.

796
00:55:28,760 --> 00:55:30,130
Veľmi pekne vám ďakujem.

797
00:55:30,140 --> 00:55:31,830
Pozri sa, či ti nič nechýba.

798
00:55:31,830 --> 00:55:32,890
Dobre.

799
00:55:35,610 --> 00:55:36,650
Je to tu.

800
00:55:37,220 --> 00:55:39,590
