845
00:58:11,960 --> 00:58:13,030
Čo?

846
00:58:14,720 --> 00:58:15,860
Áno.

847
00:58:16,760 --> 00:58:18,520
Právnička Jang sa prehrábavala mojím stolom

848
00:58:19,030 --> 00:58:21,550
