866
00:59:15,730 --> 00:59:17,280
Rýchlo. Choď za ním.

867
00:59:17,280 --> 00:59:18,550
Nechceš ho predsa stratiť.

868
00:59:20,180 --> 00:59:21,400
Ale je rýchly.

869
00:59:24,900 --> 00:59:26,180
Oh, to je...

870
00:59:27,690 --> 00:59:30,560
- Videl ste právničku Jang?
